1
00:01:49,693 --> 00:01:51,992
天哪
Dear me,

2
00:01:52,152 --> 00:01:54,592
我从来没看过这么多张拉长的脸聚在一起
I've never seen so many long faces.

3
00:01:54,652 --> 00:01:57,612
出席葬礼的传统就是要表现出悲哀
It is customary to be sad at a funeral.

4
00:01:57,622 --> 00:02:00,851
是啊，共和国已经腐朽老化
Well, the Republic is old and infirm.

5
00:02:00,871 --> 00:02:03,651
在这种时候，死亡反而是种解脱
Death can be a merciful release in such cases.

6
00:02:03,651 --> 00:02:05,711
这不是你的本意
You do not mean that.

7
00:02:05,751 --> 00:02:08,301
你不是这么想的
You don't believe that.

8
00:02:08,921 --> 00:02:11,550
你们不应该开有关独裁的玩笑
You of all people shouldn't lay jokes

9
00:02:11,590 --> 00:02:12,950
我可是认真的
 about tyranny.  Oh, I am deadly serious.

10
00:02:13,340 --> 00:02:14,700
归顺于恺撒
It is in all our interests

11
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:17,020
既符合我们的利益
to be reconciled with Caesar now,

12
00:02:17,090 --> 00:02:19,489
也是为了罗马好
for the good of Rome.

13
00:02:19,559 --> 00:02:21,959
真正的为罗马好
The good of Rome indeed.

14
00:02:22,419 --> 00:02:25,289
一旦这场闹剧结束
As soon as this... farce is done,

15
00:02:25,359 --> 00:02:27,289
我就隐退到乡下
I shall retire to the country

16
00:02:27,359 --> 00:02:29,918
看着这座城市慢慢的恢复过来
and wait for the city to come to its senses.

17
00:02:29,988 --> 00:02:32,318
这是保留尊严的唯一办法了
It is the only honorable thing to do.

18
00:02:32,688 --> 00:02:34,318
得了，我的朋友
My dear friend,

19
00:02:34,388 --> 00:02:36,318
我们早就没有尊严
we have no honor.

20
00:02:36,388 --> 00:02:38,358
如果我们还有尊严
If we had honor, we would be

21
00:02:38,418 --> 00:02:41,157
早就和卡托，西比乌一起死了
with Cato and Scipio in the afterlife.

22
00:03:10,694 --> 00:03:15,754
首先，元老院将听取马库斯·图里亚斯·西赛罗的发言
First, Senate will hear Marcus Tullius Cicero.

23
00:03:22,453 --> 00:03:26,293
在这个荣耀的凯旋庆典日之前
On this eve of his most glorious triumph,

24
00:03:26,353 --> 00:03:29,422
我推举盖乌斯·优利乌斯·恺撒
I move that Gaius Julius Caesar

25
00:03:29,492 --> 00:03:31,422
未来十年内
be made lmperator

26
00:03:31,492 --> 00:03:34,152
作为拥有无上权力的
and granted absolute power over Rome

27
00:03:34,222 --> 00:03:36,292
罗马元首
for a period of 10 years.

28
00:04:03,359 --> 00:04:05,959
正如大家所知道的
As some of you know,

29
00:04:06,029 --> 00:04:08,388
恺撒和我也有过意见不合的时候
Caesar and I have had our disagreements.

30
00:04:17,228 --> 00:04:19,687
尽管如此
However that may be,

31
00:04:19,757 --> 00:04:21,857
他还是在
he has shown himself

32
00:04:21,927 --> 00:04:24,727
胜利之后体现了他的明智和大度
to be as wise and merciful in victory

33
00:04:24,787 --> 00:04:27,856
正如他在战场上无往不胜一般
as he was invincible in battle.

34
00:04:29,396 --> 00:04:31,326
让这场内部的矛盾
Let this be an end

35
00:04:31,396 --> 00:04:35,096
早日结束吧
to division and civil strife.

36
00:04:35,156 --> 00:04:39,295
我将向恺撒献出我的忠诚
I willingly pledge my loyalty to him,

37
00:04:39,355 --> 00:04:43,125
也希望所有人都如此
and I urge you all to do the same.

38
00:04:43,195 --> 00:04:45,125
我由衷的赞成
I heartily commend

39
00:04:45,195 --> 00:04:47,124
马库斯·图里亚斯·西赛罗
the motion proposed

40
00:04:47,194 --> 00:04:49,824
提出的建议
by Marcus Tullius Cicero.

41
00:05:04,763 --> 00:05:09,462
提议得到全票通过
The motion is carried unanimously.

42
00:05:18,191 --> 00:05:20,691
在座的很多人
Many of you here today

43
00:05:20,761 --> 00:05:23,091
都曾经和我对立
fought against me.

44
00:05:24,191 --> 00:05:26,360
很多人希望看到我死
Many of you wished me dead.

45
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:29,690
也许很多现在仍然如此
Many of you perhaps still do.

46
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:32,490
但我并不介意
But I hold no grudges

47
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:35,260
也不打算报复
and seek no revenge.

48
00:05:36,759 --> 00:05:39,429
我只要求你们
I demand only this--

49
00:05:40,089 --> 00:05:43,889
和我站在一起
that you join with me

50
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:46,728
建立一个新的罗马
in building a new Rome,

51
00:05:47,358 --> 00:05:49,158
一个新的罗马
a Rome that offers

52
00:05:49,228 --> 00:05:51,758
能让他所有的公民们都
justice, peace and land

53
00:05:51,828 --> 00:05:53,758
生活在公平，和平和富饶的土地上
to all its citizens,

54
00:05:53,828 --> 00:05:56,527
而不只是那些特权阶级
not just the privileged few.

55
00:05:56,597 --> 00:05:59,457
帮助我完成这项使命
Support me in this task,

56
00:05:59,527 --> 00:06:02,157
过去的分歧都既往不咎
and old divisions will be forgotten.

57
00:06:03,227 --> 00:06:05,427
如果你反对我…
Oppose me...

58
00:06:06,826 --> 00:06:09,996
罗马将不会给你第二次机会
and Rome will not forgive you a second time.

59
00:06:12,126 --> 00:06:15,056
元老们…
Senators...

60
00:06:19,795 --> 00:06:21,795
战争已经结束
the war is over.

61
00:07:03,591 --> 00:07:05,800
女主人
Domina.

62
00:07:06,058 --> 00:07:08,026
Mmm?

63
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:10,990
朱莉娅·阿提娅来了
Atia of the Julii is here.

64
00:07:14,130 --> 00:07:16,059
阿提娅？
Atia?

65
00:07:16,129 --> 00:07:18,829
是的，已经到了
Here, now.

66
00:07:18,899 --> 00:07:21,359
她想见见你
She wishes to see you.

67
00:07:21,659 --> 00:07:24,229
阿提娅…
Atia...

68
00:07:24,299 --> 00:07:26,228
在我的房子里？
in my house?

69
00:07:36,597 --> 00:07:38,667
亲爱的阿提娅
My dear Atia.

70
00:07:40,627 --> 00:07:42,827
见到你实在太好了
How lovely to see you.

71
00:07:44,596 --> 00:07:46,596
亲爱的
Bona dea.

72
00:07:48,796 --> 00:07:50,726
我可怜的朋友
My poor friend.

73
00:07:58,735 --> 00:08:00,565
他们都对你做了些什么？
What have they done to you?

74
00:08:00,735 --> 00:08:02,665
你太客气了
You're so sweet.

75
00:08:02,735 --> 00:08:04,474
坐下吧
Come sit down.

76
00:08:06,194 --> 00:08:07,934
抱歉我没有早点来看你
I'm very sorry I haven't visited sooner,

77
00:08:07,934 --> 00:08:11,334
说实话，我是因为心情太差而没早来见你的
but to be honest, I was far too upset to face seeing you.

78
00:08:11,394 --> 00:08:14,633
一个贵妇被扒光了衣服在大街上被羞辱
The very idea, it's- it's too sinister.

79
00:08:14,693 --> 00:08:17,933
这个画面一直在我脑海中挥之不去，实在是太邪恶了
A noblewoman stripped naked and beaten on the streets--

80
00:08:17,993 --> 00:08:20,033
太可怕了，太可怕了
horrible. Horrible.

81
00:08:20,093 --> 00:08:21,933
告诉我，你现在怎么样了？
Tell me truly, how are you now?

82
00:08:21,993 --> 00:08:24,042
我恢复的很好
I'm recovering very well.

83
00:08:24,532 --> 00:08:27,092
他们找到动手的人了吗？
Have they found the culprits yet?

84
00:08:27,162 --> 00:08:30,732
还没有，不过因果报应总有时
They have not, but justice will find them eventually.

85
00:08:30,792 --> 00:08:32,792
我相信这点
I'm quite sure of that.

86
00:08:34,631 --> 00:08:36,761
要来点柠檬水么？
Would you have some lemon water?

87
00:08:38,131 --> 00:08:40,461
好的
That would be lovely.

88
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:46,330
 布鲁图斯还好吧？ 他很好
 Brutus is well, I hope.  He is.

89
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:49,860
他向我的叔叔屈服实在是太明智了
It's so wise of him to choose submission to my dear uncle.

90
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:52,200
我很怕他会为了所谓的勇猛
I was very afraid he might try

91
00:08:52,210 --> 00:08:54,839
干出一些鲁莽的事情来
some foolish act of bravery.

92
00:08:56,299 --> 00:08:59,429
男人总是会为了尊严干点蠢事
Men are so silly about their honor. No?

93
00:09:03,198 --> 00:09:05,298
我来是想问你
I've come to ask you

94
00:09:05,368 --> 00:09:07,728
你愿意在凯旋庆典时和我坐在一起吗？
if you will sit with me at the triumph.

95
00:09:07,798 --> 00:09:10,098
很多吹嘘拍马之徒都在我身边
Even though I'm being besieged by sycophants

96
00:09:10,098 --> 00:09:12,278
乞求我给他们一个位子，但我不这么想
asking for space, I thought, "No,

97
00:09:12,548 --> 00:09:14,557
我第一想到的人
if someone were to have first choice,

98
00:09:14,557 --> 00:09:16,287
就是我的好朋友赛维莉娅
it should be my dear friend Servilia

99
00:09:16,287 --> 00:09:19,727
她经历了这么多的痛苦
who's been through so much pain."

100
00:09:20,097 --> 00:09:22,796
你想的真是周到…
That is very thoughtful of you...

101
00:09:24,296 --> 00:09:26,936
但我认为我不够资格
but I think I shall not be well enough.

102
00:09:27,936 --> 00:09:29,866
真遗憾…
Well, that's a pity.

103
00:09:29,936 --> 00:09:31,536
 你真的这么想吗？ 是的
 Are you sure?  I am.

104
00:09:31,596 --> 00:09:34,665
 好吧，如果你回心转意的话… 我会告诉你的
 Well, if you change your mind-  I will let you know.

105
00:09:37,335 --> 00:09:39,935
有人告诉我奥克塔维娅离开了城里
People tell me that Octavia's left the city,

106
00:09:39,995 --> 00:09:42,194
但没人知道她去了哪
but no one knows where.

107
00:09:42,264 --> 00:09:44,164
希望别出什么事了
I hope there's nothing amiss.

108
00:09:45,364 --> 00:09:47,294
别担心
Not at all.

109
00:09:47,364 --> 00:09:49,764
她呆在我表兄在帕斯图的一幢别墅里
She's staying at my cousin's villa in Paestum,

110
00:09:49,764 --> 00:09:52,663
和一个她遇到的愚蠢的年轻诗人在一起呆着
mooning over some young fool of a poet she's met there.

111
00:09:53,003 --> 00:09:55,363
凯旋庆典之时她就会回来
She'll be back in time for the triumph.

112
00:10:17,361 --> 00:10:19,001
弟弟
Brother.

113
00:10:19,761 --> 00:10:21,680
你来这里干什么？
What are you doing here?

114
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,300
我是来带你回家的
I've come to take you home.

115
00:10:23,330 --> 00:10:25,110
 这里就是我的家  这里？
 This is my home.  This? This is not your home.

116
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:26,700
这不是你的家
I'm happy here.

117
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:28,680
我在这很愉快

118
00:10:30,370 --> 00:10:32,299
我可不相信
I don't believe you.

119
00:10:33,529 --> 00:10:35,659
无论如何，和家人在一起的地方才是你的家
In any case, your place is with your family.

120
00:10:35,689 --> 00:10:37,869
离开家庭是愚蠢的
Bad enough to run away,

121
00:10:37,929 --> 00:10:39,619
和这些人一起生活？
but to these people? This isn't the healthy way of life.

122
00:10:39,629 --> 00:10:41,318
这样的生活方式是不健康的

123
00:10:41,338 --> 00:10:43,498
你认为我们家很健康吗？
You call our family healthy?

124
00:10:43,568 --> 00:10:47,268
从大地上都能嗅出我们家的腐败
Our corruption stinks in the nostrils of Mother Earth.

125
00:10:47,278 --> 00:10:49,508
这都是那些愚蠢祭司的说法
This is your foreign priests talking.

126
00:10:51,697 --> 00:10:54,767
他们都是骗子，只是想要你的钱
They are frauds. They only want your money.

127
00:10:54,937 --> 00:10:57,797
祭司在这里不是别的，都是仆人而已
Priests are nobody. They are just servants here.

128
00:10:57,797 --> 00:10:59,697
这是圣母的领地
This is the Great Mother's house.

129
00:10:59,767 --> 00:11:02,166
圣母对我没有他求
The Great Mother wants nothing from me.

130
00:11:02,236 --> 00:11:05,266
 我在她眼中只是渺小的虫子罢了  你可不是什么虫子
 I'm a worm in her sight.  You are not a worm.

131
00:11:05,336 --> 00:11:07,536
你是朱利亚家的女儿
You are a daughter of the Julii.

132
00:11:08,016 --> 00:11:11,065
你变成这样实在让人看的心疼
It looks very ill, you running away like this.

133
00:11:11,095 --> 00:11:13,405
如果让大众知道的话
Reflects badly on the whole family

134
00:11:13,415 --> 00:11:14,835
会给我们家造成极大的不良影响
if it were known publicly.

135
00:11:17,065 --> 00:11:19,235
我还以为你是期盼我回去
For a moment I thought you wanted me back

136
00:11:19,305 --> 00:11:22,104
 是因为你很想我  别傻了
 because you missed me.  Don't be silly.

137
00:11:22,164 --> 00:11:24,364
我们都很想你
We've missed you terribly.

138
00:11:24,384 --> 00:11:26,414
母亲也很想你
Your mother has missed you.

139
00:11:26,434 --> 00:11:29,154
我相信仆人和那些小动物们也期盼着你回去
I believe even the servants and animals

140
00:11:29,154 --> 00:11:30,294
还有你？
 have missed you.  And you?

141
00:11:33,933 --> 00:11:35,903
当然还有我
And I.

142
00:11:41,032 --> 00:11:43,522
我很想你
I've missed you.

143
00:11:46,132 --> 00:11:48,732
我不能回去
I can't go back.

144
00:11:48,802 --> 00:11:50,731
已发生的事情是无法挽回的了
What's done is done.

145
00:11:50,801 --> 00:11:53,471
我原谅你了，还有母亲也原谅你
I forgive you. Your mother forgives you.

146
00:11:55,401 --> 00:11:57,341
你原谅我？
You forgive me?

147
00:11:57,401 --> 00:11:58,871
母亲原谅我？
Mother forgives me?

148
00:11:59,491 --> 00:12:02,070
如果我并不原谅你们呢？
What if I don't forgive?

149
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:03,820
不论你认为她做了什么
Whatever you think she may have done,

150
00:12:03,830 --> 00:12:08,410
想一下这都是她出于对你的爱
consider the possibility she did it out of love for you.

151
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,939
我永远不会原谅她
I'll never forgive her.

152
00:12:10,949 --> 00:12:14,399
就算是那样，你的宽恕也无关紧要
Be that as it may, your forgiveness is irrelevant.

153
00:12:14,669 --> 00:12:16,469
你必须回家
You must come home.

154
00:12:17,239 --> 00:12:18,969
对不起
I'm sorry,

155
00:12:19,539 --> 00:12:20,938
我不回去
I will not.

156
00:12:21,498 --> 00:12:24,138
我不想使用武力
I don't want to use force.

157
00:12:24,738 --> 00:12:27,438
祭司们会保护我的
The priests will protect me.

158
00:12:28,618 --> 00:12:30,137
他们不会的
They won't.

159
00:12:30,507 --> 00:12:32,537
我已经收买了他们
I've bought them.

160
00:12:32,707 --> 00:12:34,237
很便宜的价格
Quite cheaply.

161
00:12:35,807 --> 00:12:37,237
求你了
I beg you,

162
00:12:37,307 --> 00:12:39,336
让我留在这里吧
Iet me stay here.

163
00:12:43,546 --> 00:12:45,226
你都干了些什么？
What have you done?

164
00:12:53,235 --> 00:12:54,935
艾文泰的居民们
Fellow citizens of the Aventine!

165
00:12:58,765 --> 00:13:01,004
居民们
Fellow citizens!

166
00:13:03,734 --> 00:13:06,234
艾文泰的居民们
Fellow citizens of the Aventine!

167
00:13:08,274 --> 00:13:11,733
我的名字是卢西尔斯·乌瑞纳斯
My name is Lucius vorenus,

168
00:13:11,803 --> 00:13:15,073
斯特拉提纳族人，第13军团的退伍军人
tribe of Stellatina, veteran of the 1 3th Legion.

169
00:13:15,073 --> 00:13:18,373
你们中的某些人也许认识我
Some of you may know me.

170
00:13:18,802 --> 00:13:21,242
我给你们带来了好消息
I bring you good news.

171
00:13:21,302 --> 00:13:24,872
恺撒已经结束了贵族们的苛政
Caesar has put an end to patrician tyranny,

172
00:13:24,932 --> 00:13:27,302
他确定民众们的声音
and will ensure that the common people

173
00:13:27,322 --> 00:13:29,411
 将会再次得到尊重  滚回高卢去吧
 be heard once more.  Go back to Gaul, ginger knob.

174
00:13:29,471 --> 00:13:31,111
生姜头

175
00:13:32,641 --> 00:13:35,601
我不会否认，我的朋友我的外表看起来的确是高卢人
I'll not deny it, friend, I have a Gallic look about me,

176
00:13:35,671 --> 00:13:37,901
但我确实是个罗马人
but I'm as solid Roman as you are.

177
00:13:37,971 --> 00:13:40,270
我为罗马抛头颅撒热血
I've shed blood for Rome.

178
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:42,270
我的父亲也为罗马浴血奋战
My father shed blood for Rome,

179
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:44,940
我的祖父和曾祖父同样如此
as did his father and his father before him.

180
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:48,469
我的妻子，是在这里出生的，在艾文泰
My wife- my wife was born here in the Aventine!

181
00:13:48,539 --> 00:13:51,639
我和这里的所有其它人一样，是一个罗马人
I am as solid a Roman as any man here!

182
00:13:55,409 --> 00:13:59,108
如果我被选为你们的地区长官
If I am elected as your local magistrate,

183
00:13:59,138 --> 00:14:01,168
我以朱庇特石的名义起誓
I promise on Jupiter's stone

184
00:14:01,238 --> 00:14:03,538
努力创造出一个和平
